{"title_page": "Asim Azhar", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{short description|Pakistani singer, songwriter, and actor|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Asim Azhar\n| image              = https://www.instagram.com/p/B8T5_LgF2Wp/ \n[[File:www.superstarsbio.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Asim-Azhar.jpg|thumb]]\n| caption            = \n| birth_name         = \n| birth_date         = {{birth date and age|1996|10|29|df=yes}}<ref>Asim Azhar Age, Height, Family, GF, Biography & More</ref>\n| birth_place        = [[Karachi]], Pakistan\n| alma_mater         = \n| occupation         = Singer, songwriter, musician\n| notable_works      = [[Coke Studio (Pakistani season 8)|Coke Studio Season 8]]<br>[[Coke Studio (Pakistani season 9)|Coke Studio Season 9]]<br>[[Coke Studio (Pakistani season 11)|Coke Studio Season 11]]\n| spouse            = none\n| parents            = Azhar Hussain (father)<br>[[Gul-e-Rana]] (mother)\n}}\n\n'''Asim Azhar''' ({{lang-ur|{{nastaliq|'''\u0639\u0627\u0635\u0645 \u0627\u0638\u06c1\u0631'''}}}}) is a Pakistani singer, songwriter, and actor who is often referred to as the ''Justin Bieber of Pakistan'' however he is not because of his lack of talent compared to Justin Bieber. due to his stardom in early age.<ref name=\"auto\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1445796|title=THE ICON INTERVIEW: ASIM AZHAR\u2019S LIFE LESSONS|first=Maliha|last=Rehman|date=18 November 2018|website=Dawn|location=Pakistan}}</ref> He started his career as a singer on YouTube, re-singing contemporary Western songs before he became a public figure.<ref name=\"auto\"/>. When the cross-border situation worsened, Azhar's plans with his record company, Universal Music India came to a halt.He recently received The Best Stylish Performer award at PSA in Dubai.\nBorn to Azhar Hussain, and actress [[Gul-e-Rana]].<ref>{{cite news|title=To work with Shah Rukh Khan is a dream I have to accomplish: Asim Azhar|url=http://zeenews.india.com/exclusive/to-work-with-shah-rukh-khan-is-a-dream-i-have-to-accomplish-asim-azhar_1579759.html|accessdate=23 September 2017|work=Zee News|date=16 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Meet Coke Studio stars Asim Azhar and Rachel Viccaji|url=https://www.geo.tv/latest/114789-Meet-Coke-Studio-stars-Asim-Azhar-and-Rachel-Viccaji|accessdate=23 September 2017|work=geo.tv}}</ref> He became popular because of his songs recorded in [[Coke Studio (Pakistan)|Coke Studio 9]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://tribune.com.pk/story/1600442/4-musicians-spoilt-actors-asim-azhar/|title=Asim Azhar \u2013 interview to Tribune.com.pk|date=4 January 2018|work=Tribune.com.pk {{!}} Pakistani Songs & Drama  Reviews {{!}} Ratings {{!}} Celebrities {{!}} Entertainment news Portal|access-date=11 March 2018}}</ref>\n<ref name=cokestudio>[http://www.cokestudio.com.pk/season8/asim-azhar.html?WT.cl=1&WT.mn=Artists%20-%20Asim%20Azhar Profile of Asim Azhar on Coke Studio Pakistan website] Retrieved 20 March 2018</ref>\n<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/music/artists/2b2bce6f-e3ce-472c-bcfb-93d9cc0d08f1 Asim Azhar Tracks on BBC Music website] Retrieved 20 March 2018</ref>\n\n==Discography==\n===Singles===\n*2013\n** \"Whistle\"\n** \"The A Team\"\n*2014\n** \"Maahi Aaja\"\n** \"Patakha Guddi\"\n** \"Hands in the Air\" \n** \"Sunlay\"\n** \"Soniye\" \n*2017\n** \"Khuwahish\" \n** \"Teriyaan\" \u2013 co-singer with [[Aima Baig]]\n*2018\n** \"Jo Tu Na Mila\"\n*2019\n** \"Humrahi\"\n** \"Tere Liye\"\n\n===Soundtracks===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Song\n! Music\n! Notes\n|-\n|2016\n|\"Anabia\"\n|Saajna\n|Qasim Azhar\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|2017\n|''[[Pagli (TV series)|Pagli]]''\n|\"Ek Pagli Hai Ye\"\n|\n|co-singer [[Aima Baig]]\n|-\n|Noor \n|Noor\n|\n|\n|-\n|\"Tere Bina\"\n|\"Tere Bina\"\n|\n|co-singer [[Sara Haider]]\n|-\n|\"[[Balu Mahi]]\"\n|\"[[Balu Mahi]]\"\n|\n|co-singer [[Aima Baig]]\t\n|-\n|2019\n|Ehd e wafa\n|Ehd e wafa OST\n|[[Sahir Ali Bagga]]\n|With [[Ali Zafar]], Sahir Ali Bagga & Aima Bai