d Whalers || rowspan=\"2\" | [[Toronto Maple Leafs]]\n|-\n| 28. || [[Stan Weir]] (D) || rowspan=\"2\" | Edmonton Oilers\n|-\n| 29. || [[John Hughes (ice hockey b. 1954)|John Hughes]] (D) ||[[Vancouver Canucks]]\n|-\n| 30. || [[Paul MacKinnon]] (D) || Winnipeg Jets || [[Washington Capitals]]\n|}\n*''Twelve additional players were reclaimed, but were chosen as 'Priority Selections' by the four merging franchises''\n\n==Expansion draft results==\n\n===Priority selections===\n\n''These players were \"priority selections\" in the 1979 NHL Expansion Draft.''\n\n{| border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"wikitable sortable sortable\" style=\"width:80%\"\n|-\n\n!style=\"background:#F87A36;\" width=5%|No.\n!!width=15% style=\"background:#F87A36;\"|Player\n!!width=4% style=\"background:#F87A36;\"|Rights Denied\n!!width=6% style=\"background:#F87A36;\"|Rights Kept\n|-\n| 1. || [[Dave Dryden]] ([[Goaltender|G]]) || [[Buffalo Sabres]] || rowspan=\"4\" | [[Edmonton Oilers]]\n|-\n| 2. || [[Wayne Gretzky]] ([[centre (ice hockey)|C]]) || -- \n|-\n| 3. || [[Bengt-\u00c5ke Gustafsson|Bengt-Ake Gustafsson]]<sup>1</sup> ([[winger (ice hockey)|RW]]) || [[Washington Capitals]] \n|-\n| 4. || [[Eddie Mio]] (G) || [[Minnesota North Stars]] \n|-\n| 5. || [[Jordy Douglas]] ([[forward (ice hockey)|F]]) || [[Toronto Maple Leafs]] || rowspan=\"3\" | [[Hartford Whalers]]\n|-\n| 6. || [[John Garrett (ice hockey)|John Garrett]] (G) || [[St. Louis Blues]] \n|-\n| 7. || [[Mark Howe]] ([[defenceman (ice hockey)|D]]) || [[Boston Bruins]] \n|-\n| 8. || [[Paul Baxter]] (D) || [[Pittsburgh Penguins]] || rowspan=\"3\" | [[Quebec Nordiques]]\n|-\n| 9. || [[Richard Brodeur]] (G) || [[New York Islanders]] \n|-\n|10. || [[Garry Lariviere]] (D) || Buffalo Sabres \n|-\n|11. || [[Scott Campbell (ice hockey b. 1957)|Scott Campbell]] (D) || St. Louis Blues || rowspan=\"3\" | [[Winnipeg Jets (1972\u201396)|Winnipeg Jets]]\n|-\n|12. || [[Morris Lukowich]] ([[winger (ice hockey)|LW]]) || [[Pittsburgh Penguins]] \n|-\n|13. || [[Markus Mattsson]] (G) || New York Islanders \n|}\n\n<small><sup>1</sup> The NHL denied the Oilers' claim of Bengt Gustafsson.  League president [[John Ziegler (ice hockey)|John Ziegler]] ruled that the Oilers violated WHA rules when they attempted to add Gustafsson to their team during the 1979 playoffs, so they voided any claim on him.<ref>[http://washingtoncapitalslegends.blogspot.ca/2007/07/bengt-ake-gustafsson.html Capitals claim on Gustafsson]</ref></small>\n\n''These are players selected in the 1979 NHL Expansion Draft.''\n\n===Edmonton Oilers selections<ref name=bluepucks/>===\n\n{| border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"wikitable sortable sortable\" style=\"width:80%\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#00205B; color:#FFFFFF; border:2px solid #CF4520;\" width=\"2%\"|#\n! style=\"background:#00205B; color:#FFFFFF; border:2px solid #CF4520;\" width=\"9%\"|Player\n! style=\"background:#00205B; color:#FFFFFF; border:2px solid #CF4520;\" width=\"9%\"|Drafted from\n|-\n| 1. || [[Cam Connor]] ([[winger (ice hockey)|RW]]) || [[Montreal Canadiens]]\n|-\n| 2. || [[Lee Fogolin]] ([[defenceman (ice hockey)|D]]) || [[Buffalo Sabres]]\n|-\n| 3. || [[Pat Price (ice hockey)|Pat Price]] (D) || [[New York Islanders]]\n|-\n| 4. || [[Colin Campbell (ice hockey executive)|Colin Campbell]] (D) || [[Pittsburgh Penguins]]\n|-\n| 5. || [[Larry Brown (ice hockey)|Larry Brown]] (D) || [[Los Angeles Kings]]\n|-\n| 6. || [[Pete LoPresti]] ([[Goaltender|G]]) || [[Minnesota North Stars]]\n|-\n| 7. || [[Ron Areshenkoff]] ([[centre (ice hockey)|C]]) || Buffalo Sabres\n|-\n| 8. || [[Inge Hammarstr\u00f6m|Inge Hammarstrom]] (D) || [[St. Louis Blues]]\n|-\n|9. || [[John Gould (ice hockey)|John Gould]] (RW) || [[Atlanta Flames]]\n|-\n|10. || [[Doug Hicks]] (D) || [[Chicago Blackhawks|Chicago Black Hawks]]\n|-\n|11. || [[Tom Edur]] (D) || rowspan=\"2\" | Pittsburgh Penguins\n|-\n|12. || [[Wayne Bianchin]] ([[winger (ice hockey)|LW]]) \n|-\n|13. || [[Mike Forbe